    <item>
      <title>Ruby 3.3.0 is available</title>
      <link>https://stagingv6.cleverapps.io/developers/changelog/2024-01-24-ruby-3.3.0/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://stagingv6.cleverapps.io/developers/changelog/2024-01-24-ruby-3.3.0/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;You can now choose the &lt;code&gt;3.3.0&lt;/code&gt; release of Ruby when you deploy Ruby on Rails applications on Clever Cloud. It can be set either through your &lt;code&gt;Gemfile&lt;/code&gt; or the &lt;code&gt;CC_RUBY_VERSION&lt;/code&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://developers.clever-cloud.com/doc/reference/reference-environment-variables/#ruby&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;environment variable&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn more about Ruby 3.3.0 release &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.ruby-lang.org/en/news/2023/12/25/ruby-3-3-0-released/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;





  












